xxl.core.predicates

Class Or<P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.predicates.AbstractPredicate<P>
      • xxl.core.predicates.BinaryPredicate<P>
        • xxl.core.predicates.Or<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of the predicate's parameters.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Predicate<P>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GreaterEqual, LessEqual

    public class Or<P>
extends BinaryPredicate<P>
    This class provides a logical OR predicate. The OR predicate represents the disjunction of two predicates to a new predicate that returns false if and only if both underlying predicates return false.
    See Also:
